{"tid":2504542,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"兩人被控向民建聯辦事處縱火 首被告今缺席聆訊 次被告還柙候判","createTime":"2021-04-26T03:14:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-26T10:42:00.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"f36232bb7daf4094e802e788fee43ea50860f355","tid":2504542,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T03:14:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15256\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F15256&d=D9q%2FqAhMrjKrs4nvjauepDC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=f1b31ced\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15256</a><br />\n<br />\n#區域法院第廿四庭<br />\n#練錦鴻法官 #審訊 [1/5]<br />\nD1:李(27) 🛑曾還押逾一個月<br />\nD2:15歲少年 #1123粉嶺 <br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n(1) 縱火 [D1&amp;D2]<br />\n違反香港法例第200章《刑事罪行條例》第60(1)(3)及63(1)條。控罪詳情指D1李手足及D2於2019年11月23日在粉嶺華心邨華勉樓地下2號鋪姚銘區議員辦事處，用火損壞屬於該辦事處的財產，即一幅2米x3米的牆壁、1把抽氣扇、2部閉路電視攝影機、2塊告示版。<br />\n<br />\n(2) 縱火 <br />\n各被告被控於同日同地無合理辯解或意圖而用火損壞2米乘3米的牆壁。 <br />\n<br />\n案情大綱：落選民建聯前區議員姚銘位於華心邨的辦事處，在區議會選舉前夕遭縱火，警方約凌晨3時許接報後立即翻查閉路電視，約兩小時後在華心邨拘捕二人。在李身上搜出打火機及易燃液體，惟未在少年身上搜獲任何物品。 <br />\n<br />\n--------------------------<br />\n🛑首被告缺席聆訊，辯方律師自2021年4月13日後已經無法聯絡D1，向法庭申請不再代表他，他的母親在4月15日報警稱兒子失蹤；法庭接納控方申請，將D1的$30,000保釋金充公並發出拘捕令。 <br />\n<br />\n🙇&zwj;♂️D2選擇認罪，由於控方未準備好案情，審訊押後至今日14:30繼續，期間交由懲教看管。"},{"pid":"f552c6e7cf3c9320b1e7eb4ce610e8c6d2933e61","tid":2504542,"uid":54876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T03:16:28.000Z","msg":"練官咁多案審嘅？"},{"pid":"60708bd9537727b790cace855747f9b9d4f2e0ea","tid":2504542,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T03:23:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a89e7c2041b4fdca64c2bd100425acba12f6919f","tid":2504542,"uid":117276,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T03:25:10.000Z","msg":"希望手足走到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a01ea6203f9a758171de81cce6e78b5399c73c5f","tid":2504542,"uid":52705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T03:27:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d73a9b2418c8d71e4194d5ab9ae1709f7ba84c82","tid":2504542,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T03:29:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf8a53a71a075a27e81485f1a85a8822fa122e4c","tid":2504542,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f552c6e7cf3c9320b1e7eb4ce610e8c6d2933e61","tid":2504542,"uid":54876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T03:16:28.000Z","msg":"練官咁多案審嘅？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T03:30:03.000Z","msg":"夠紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fece17170d465c566d88c2196ba65625e64c864","tid":2504542,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T03:31:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9645004d1dd016cc12086d16afee382faa38ede","tid":2504542,"uid":110043,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T03:33:39.000Z","msg":"見到係練狗審<br />\n走得好<br />\n祝生活愉快"},{"pid":"9622cc77ca60dbdb792f24a78993d4ad9df9afd1","tid":2504542,"uid":333488,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T03:38:53.000Z","msg":"離唔開香港其實都好難，實有一日賴嘢，希望佢可以出海釣魚，漂流左去其他地方啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba8f5699888445103d3e97a1d3e9b425e5bb9b96","tid":2504542,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T03:39:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/mask.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7656f019db8bf06b83c62ac1cae771ee7a844f19","tid":2504542,"uid":110043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T03:40:48.000Z","msg":"走得好"},{"pid":"e17db4c0dee9f9a418d109df4477b2545b54a715","tid":2504542,"uid":87985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T03:54:42.000Z","msg":"今日幾單認罪"},{"pid":"4665bcb0a1c536ff37c525c08e51dc406797dd1d","tid":2504542,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T04:33:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5acf0322b83c5ae0d969e51416b8671a480c9207","tid":2504542,"uid":260121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T04:38:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8708709b962d156b570440d3b20518301fa2009c","tid":2504542,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T04:58:31.000Z","msg":"前年11.24區議會選舉前夕，民建聯北區區議員姚銘的辦事處凌晨時分遭兩名黑衫人縱火，警方其後在附近拘捕一名大專生及一名14歲男生，及後控以兩項縱火罪。案件原定今日在區域法院開審，惟大專生缺席聆訊，法官練錦鴻頒下拘捕令，至於同案未成年男生則透過代表大狀表示會認罪。控方需時處理案情，聆訊下午繼續。<br />\n<br />\n27歲被告案發時在明愛專上學院就讀社工系。代表李的女大狀今早指出，她與律師團隊跟李最後一次見面是本月13日，當時李需要到律師樓開會。李母則於本月18日報警，稱與李失去聯絡。法官練錦鴻頒下拘捕令，並充公李的3萬元保釋金。<br />\n<br />\n李與同案14歲少年被告被控兩項縱火罪，兩人分別被指於前年11月17日及23日在粉嶺華心邨華勉樓地下焚燒姚銘區議員辦事處的牆壁、告示板及閉路電視攝影機。<br />\n<br />\n本案14歲男生首次提堂後獲准保釋，惟現時已還柙。李則於案件首度提堂後不獲保釋，還柙37天後，前年12月30日獲高等法院法官李運騰批准保釋，可以繼續學業及回家過除夕，惟其間須每天向警署報到兩次，以及遵守宵禁令。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210426/ZQI7OJ5J3VCCFABXZB2JZ4TI6U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210426%2FZQI7OJ5J3VCCFABXZB2JZ4TI6U%2F&d=D9q%2FqAhMrjKrs4nvjauepDC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=752198aa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210426%2FZQI7OJ5J3VCCFABXZB2JZ4TI6U%2F&h=45038c96\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210426/ZQI7OJ5J3VCCFABXZB2JZ4TI6U/</a>"},{"pid":"0b0abd30d05521b83d0706739849047586e06b2f","tid":2504542,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T05:01:17.000Z","msg":"連燈軍師最支持呢d行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0999e5277bd9338b95762484e54bc89821e5ea21","tid":2504542,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T05:02:01.000Z","msg":"練狗屌你老母"},{"pid":"8eb801e951a1316e693173f70b0ac7559d649946","tid":2504542,"uid":57205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f552c6e7cf3c9320b1e7eb4ce610e8c6d2933e61","tid":2504542,"uid":54876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T03:16:28.000Z","msg":"練官咁多案審嘅？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T05:03:24.000Z","msg":"根正苗紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dd3d80286777b190b7bf3d66f0f44839367da4e","tid":2504542,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T06:44:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e54fc9101ec310a56f12c61a2a868c8e959ddb9","tid":2504542,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T06:47:30.000Z","msg":"李運騰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"233a1c891e78199b5dcb80ee207a741fddf00c32","tid":2504542,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T09:03:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210426/RNFM3S5T4VDSPMUOPTRO3MDJQM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210426%2FRNFM3S5T4VDSPMUOPTRO3MDJQM%2F&d=D9q%2FqAhMrjKrs4nvjauepDC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=16ca4630\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210426%2FRNFM3S5T4VDSPMUOPTRO3MDJQM%2F&h=52c656c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210426/RNFM3S5T4VDSPMUOPTRO3MDJQM/</a>"},{"pid":"19740fe079cc7982e59a806f6482becbb174a675","tid":2504542,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T09:59:46.000Z","msg":"警方約在兩小時後離開案發辦事處，發現兩名被告步向他們，於是截停兩人，在其中一身上找到打火機、手套及有打火機油助燃劑的黑色罐，又在少年被告身上找到手套及黑頸巾。<span class=\"red\">少年被告接受警誡時稱一時貪玩才縱火。</span><br />\n<br />\n法官練錦鴻先索閱男生背景、勞教中心及教導所報告，還柙候判。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林奠又話認錯肯俾警師警戒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e044f4a48c0463ea3e7838dcf69ce442519d921","tid":2504542,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T10:33:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ec7c77707a9d4a230c5075f5100ed6cc9c55224","tid":2504542,"uid":260694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T10:35:50.000Z","msg":"放火係好事嚟"}]}